en_361330_0	The 4th day of the mock Field Training Exercise (FTX), 'Cormorant Strike' this morning (9) at Welikanda Railway Station launched a mock operation to demonstrate how two insurgents hiding in a train compartment were apprehended following intelligence received by the troops under training from an informant.
en_361330_1	For this, two Special Forces rider teams responded with their maximum capabilities in support of four Urban fighting teams including foreign troops.
en_361330_2	During this mock operation, troops effectively arrested those two insurgents with minimum force but with manoeuvrist approach.
